comment: Omar Khayyam lived from May 1048 - December 1131 (That's the 11th and 12th centuries!) The Battle of Hastings occurred on October 14, 1066 (That's the 11th century.) SO......... I love how it's Amber Heard's own tattoo, and a conversation she knew to prepare for ahead of time, yet she still attributes Omar Khayyam to the wrong century! On the other hand, Seth MacFarlane was witty enough to mock her pretentiousness by coming up with the Battle of Hastings off the top of his head, then mock her pretentiousness again by correcting himself (the 11th, not 10th century). Clearly he's more knowledgeable than she is, yet he's not the one being showy about it. He's actually making off the cuff jokes about ostentatiousness and, wow, this is just really brilliant and subtle humor at its finest.
